guest_message: Hi there, I'm Sofia Russo. I'm thinking of ordering some food today. Could you tell me more about your appetizers? I'm in the mood for something that goes well with wine!

These are some great choices! I think I'll go with the Spinach Artichoke Dip to start. Also, could you tell me more about your spaghetti options? I'm considering something along those lines for my main. Thanks!
Oh, the Spaghetti Carbonara sounds perfect for me! I'll stick with that, but can you add some extra Parmesan for that rich flavor? Thanks!
Thanks for confirming my order! I'm actually all set with my food choices, and I'm ready to enjoy them without any drinks this time. Appreciate the suggestion though!
My name is Sofia Russo. Thanks for confirming the order, I'll be there in 20 minutes for pickup!
